00:05:52,670 --> 00:05:55,130
<font color="yellow">"but he's a very inspiring person."</font>

94
00:05:56,170 --> 00:05:57,270
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

95
00:05:58,730 --> 00:05:59,930
<font color="yellow">my observations...</font>

96
