<font color="yellow">from the last few years tell me that the mayor, Mr Chun Gab Soo,</font>

97
00:06:04,570 --> 00:06:05,930
<font color="yellow">isn't that kind of person.</font>

98
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:10,200
<font color="yellow">It could hurt his career significantly...</font>

99
00:06:10,770 --> 00:06:12,430
<font color="yellow">to the point that it's not revivable.</font>

100
