<font color="yellow">and Mr Park Sang Ho,</font>

105
00:06:26,930 --> 00:06:28,870
<font color="yellow">I know that it is the right thing to do.</font>

106
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:32,870
<font color="yellow">Power...</font>

107
00:06:33,830 --> 00:06:36,230
<font color="yellow">should not be used to hurt people.</font>

108
00:06:37,770 --> 00:06:40,700
<font color="yellow">It should be used to protect the people who have been wounded.</font>

109
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:49,670
<font color="yellow">Are you sure that you won't regret it?</font>

110
00:06:51,970 --> 00:06:53,700
<font color="yellow">Make me not regret my decision.</font>

