<font color="yellow">Your granddaughter should be home soon.</font>

141
00:08:54,670 --> 00:08:56,170
<font color="yellow">Go home to her.</font>

142
00:08:56,870 --> 00:08:59,900
<font color="yellow">Go on home. Bye.</font>

143
00:09:07,300 --> 00:09:09,540
<font color="yellow">Did you have to be so cold?</font>

