<font color="yellow">What?</font>

145
00:09:12,970 --> 00:09:16,570
<font color="yellow">He came a long way just to see you.</font>

146
00:09:17,130 --> 00:09:18,500
<font color="yellow">You were too mean.</font>

147
00:09:19,070 --> 00:09:20,100
<font color="yellow">He visits so often.</font>

148
00:09:21,430 --> 00:09:23,170
<font color="yellow">There's nothing I can do.</font>

149
00:09:25,300 --> 00:09:27,850
<font color="yellow">I'm on the management support team.</font>

150
00:09:27,850 --> 00:09:30,540
<font color="yellow">- We can't stop redevelopment...
