151
00:09:31,800 --> 00:09:33,900
<font color="yellow">That old man, Mr Woo Sang Chul.</font>

152
00:09:35,170 --> 00:09:37,300
<font color="yellow">Doesn't he remind you of someone?</font>

153
00:09:43,670 --> 00:09:44,670
<font color="yellow">Mr Park Sang Ho.</font>

154
00:09:47,700 --> 00:09:49,270
<font color="yellow">Doesn't he come to mind...</font>

155
00:09:49,870 --> 00:09:51,370
<font color="yellow">when you see that old man?</font>

156
00:09:52,230 --> 00:09:53,230
<font color="yellow">Give me a discount.</font>

157
00:09:54,370 --> 00:09:55,430
<font color="yellow">Please.</font>

158
00:10:03,670 --> 00:10:06,270
<font color="yellow">People like them come to us...</font>

159
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:08,870
<font color="yellow">because they have no one else to talk to.</font>

160
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:13,100
<font color="yellow">They have a lot to say but no one to talk to.</font>

161
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:16,800
<font color="yellow">That's why they come to us.</font>

162
00:10:19,430 --> 00:10:22,130
<font color="yellow">Can't you hear him out?</font>

163
00:10:22,870 --> 00:10:25,300
<font color="yellow">It's not that hard to just listen.</font>

164
00:10:27,430 --> 00:10:28,470
<font color="yellow">To be frank,</font>

165
00:10:29,430 --> 00:10:32,170
<font color="yellow">if that old man were to end up like Sang Ho,</font>

166
00:10:33,670 --> 00:10:35,400
