00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:45,400
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

170
00:10:46,430 --> 00:10:49,570
<font color="yellow">What happens to him is none of my business.</font>

171
00:10:50,040 --> 00:10:51,230
<font color="yellow">Why should I care...</font>

172
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:54,100
<font color="yellow">what happens to him?</font>

173
00:10:54,540 --> 00:10:55,730
<font color="yellow">We aren't related.</font>

174
00:10:56,570 --> 00:10:57,570
<font color="yellow">Are we?</font>

175
00:11:01,970 --> 00:11:04,000
<font color="yellow">What happened to you, Sir?</font>

176
00:11:05,230 --> 00:11:06,800
<font color="yellow">Nothing's happened.</font>

177
00:11:07,670 --> 00:11:09,270
<font color="yellow">This is who I am.</font>

178
00:11:11,030 --> 00:11:13,050
<font color="yellow">Don't call me sir.</font>

179
00:11:13,050 --> 00:11:16,700
<font color="yellow">I'm on the management support team. I'm no longer your chief.</font>

180
00:11:17,270 --> 00:11:18,270
<font color="yellow">Am I?</font>

181
00:11:19,070 --> 00:11:20,400
<font color="yellow">You're the chief now.</font>

182
00:12:03,030 --> 00:12:04,600
<font color="yellow">Shall we talk outside?</font>

183
00:12:05,130 --> 00:12:06,230
<font color="yellow">It's a hot day.</font>

184
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:14,670
<font color="yellow">So,</font>

185
00:12:15,300 --> 00:12:17,230
<font color="yellow">that Baek Sung Il guy.</font>

186
00:12:18,170 --> 00:12:19,530
<font color="yellow">What is he up to these days?</font>

187
00:12:22,270 --> 00:12:23,870
<font color="yellow">I'm getting regular updates.</font>

188
00:12:25,300 --> 00:12:27,270
<font color="yellow">You won't have to worry about him.</font>

189
00:12:30,030 --> 00:12:32,100
<font color="yellow">He's quiet and gets into no trouble.</font>

190
00:12:35,070 --> 00:12:36,230
<font color="yellow">That's good.</font>

191
00:12:39,930 --> 00:12:41,470
<font color="yellow">Mr Mayor.</font>

192
00:12:42,070 --> 00:12:45,830
<font color="yellow">Redeveloping the Maseok-dong plot.</font>

193
00:12:46,570 --> 00:12:48,530
<font color="yellow">Do you hate the idea that much?</font>

194
00:12:52,170 --> 00:12:53,370
<font color="yellow">It's the area...</font>

195
00:12:54,770 --> 00:12:56,970
<font color="yellow">that pays the least amount of taxes.</font>

196
00:12:57,770 --> 00:12:58,800
<font color="yellow">Maseok-dong.</font>

197
00:13:02,070 --> 00:13:06,070
<font color="yellow">The poorest area in Seowon City.</font>

198
00:13:07,700 --> 00:13:11,300
<font color="yellow">That explains why all the landowners dress so poorly.</font>

199
00:13:12,570 --> 00:13:16,400
<font color="yellow">You can tell right away that it's a run-down neighbourhood.</font>

200
00:13:20,670 --> 00:13:21,800
<font color="yellow">Isn't that why...</font>

201
00:13:22,800 --> 00:13:25,300
<font color="yellow">you sold it to me for almost nothing?</font>

202
00:13:25,670 --> 00:13:27,200
<font color="yellow">All the buildings there.</font>

203
00:13:27,770 --> 00:13:29,900
<font color="yellow">The landlords and landladies aren't the problem.</font>

204
00:13:30,570 --> 00:13:32,030
<font color="yellow">It's the tenants.</font>

205
00:13:33,570 --> 00:13:37,430
<font color="yellow">If we remove them by force, they will become homeless.</font>

206
00:13:38,070 --> 00:13:42,400
<font color="yellow">I can't give up on my right just for your pity.</font>

207
00:13:43,170 --> 00:13:44,170
<font color="yellow">I will...</font>

208
00:13:44,500 --> 00:13:47,800
<font color="yellow">exercise my right.</font>

209
00:13:49,970 --> 00:13:51,670
<font color="yellow">Did I not compensate them?</font>

210
00:13:53,170 --> 00:13:54,630
<font color="yellow">Did I not give them time?</font>

211
00:13:54,970 --> 00:13:56,070
<font color="yellow">I gave them both.</font>

